videos.headline: UCLA's Brown caps off impressive TD drive
videos.description: Britain Brown caps off UCLA's drive down the field by scoring a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA's Brown caps off impressive TD drive) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon gets the pick after Thompson-Robinson's arm is hit
videos.description: Dorian Thompson-Robinson's arm is hit as he's throwing, and the pass gets picked off by DJ James.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oregon gets the pick after Thompson-Robinson's arm is hit) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA capitalizes on blocked punt with a TD
videos.description: UCLA gets great field position after blocking a punt, and they would capitalize as Kazmeir Allen hauls in a 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA capitalizes on blocked punt with a TD) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Devon Williams' impressive catch sets up Oregon's TD
videos.description: Devon Williams goes over the defender for an impressive 32-yard catch, and Travis Dye capitalizes for the Ducks with a short touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Devon Williams' impressive catch sets up Oregon's TD) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dye turns the corner for 2nd TD of the day
videos.description: Travis Dye gets to the outside and turns up field for the 4-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dye turns the corner for 2nd TD of the day) 2021/10/23 ESHEEET

videos.headline: Hutson's catch sets up Dye's 3rd TD of the day
videos.description: Kris Hutson gets Oregon inside the one with a 16-yard catch. The next play Travis Dye plows into the end zone for his third touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hutson's catch sets up Dye's 3rd TD of the day) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA punter drops snap giving Oregon the ball
videos.description: Oregon is set up in UCLA territory after punter Stefan Flintoft drops the snap and the Ducks recover.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA punter drops snap giving Oregon the ball) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dye's 4th TD puts Oregon up 10
videos.description: Oregon takes a 10-point lead after Travis Dye rushes for his fourth touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dye's 4th TD puts Oregon up 10) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hutson's fumble sets UCLA up in Oregon territory
videos.description: UCLA has the ball in Oregon territory after Jay Shaw recovers the Kris Hutson fumble and returns it to the 20.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hutson's fumble sets UCLA up in Oregon territory) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anthony Brown takes off for 43-yard TD run
videos.description: Oregon quarterback Anthony Brown bursts through the line and is gone for a 43-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Anthony Brown takes off for 43-yard TD run) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson-Robinson spins into end zone for UCLA TD
videos.description: UCLA cuts into Oregon's lead after Dorian Thompson-Robinson spins into the end zone for the 2-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Thompson-Robinson spins into end zone for UCLA TD) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA capitalizes on INT to cut Oregon's lead to 3
videos.description: UCLA gets closer as they turn an interception into a Brittain Brown touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA capitalizes on INT to cut Oregon's lead to 3) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA gets huge INT in the end zone
videos.description: UCLA's Jay Shaw picks off the pass in the end zone, giving UCLA the ball back late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA gets huge INT in the end zone) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: DJ James clinches Oregon win with an INT
videos.description: DJ James steps in front of the pass for the interception, clinching the win for Oregon vs. UCLA.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (DJ James clinches Oregon win with an INT) 2021/10/23 ESHEET
